metadata.description: Ronald McDonald ate too much food and McDonald's. Now he looks like this. Maybe that's why you don't see him in any advertisements anymore. I (Nathan Collins) painted this image myself! I hope you like it! If you buy, then message me and I'll send you a physical copy as well.Â
